FT  17 SEP 92 / International Company News: Lloyd's location for US insurer
AMERICAN International Group, one of the largest US composite insurers, said
yesterday that it had reached an agreement with Lloyd's of London, the UK
insurance market, to set up the first insurance company underwriting
operation located at Lloyd's.
Lloyd's confirmed it is in discussions with up to 20 insurance companies
about rental space on the third floor of its building.
